@startuml
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #F7FCFF
    BorderColor #88BBDD
    FontSize 12
}

note over App, VFS
打开软链接关键：靠inode->i_mode == S_IFLNK识别软链接
1.dentry找到inode，读取i_mode判定类型
2.是S_IFLNK则读取inode数据区的目标路径
3.VFS自动递归路径查找原文件inode
end note

box "【用户态 User Space】" #LightYellow
actor App
end box

box "【内核态 Kernel Space】" #LightCyan
participant "VFS 虚拟文件系统" as VFS
participant "symlink_inode" as SymInode
participant "real_inode" as RealInode
participant "file结构体" as File
end box

App -> VFS: <color:red>①</color> open("/b/sym.txt",O_RDONLY)
activate VFS

VFS -> SymInode: <color:red>②</color> 路径解析拿到软链接inode
activate SymInode
SymInode -> SymInode: <color:red>③</color> 校验i_mode == S_IFLNK
note right: <color:red>内核从此处识别是软链接，关键判断点</color>
SymInode --> VFS: 取出inode内保存的路径:/a/real.txt
deactivate SymInode

VFS -> VFS: <color:red>④</color> 重新解析真实路径/a/real.txt
VFS -> RealInode: <color:red>⑤</color> 获取原文件inode
activate RealInode
RealInode --> VFS: 普通文件inode(S_IFREG)
deactivate RealInode

VFS -> File: <color:red>⑥</color> 新建file绑定真实inode
activate File
File --> VFS
deactivate File

VFS --> App: <color:red>⑦</color> 返回fd，fd关联真实文件
deactivate VFS
@enduml